              </p>
            </li>

            <li permid="pnE">
              <p permid="aOA">
                Find the number of different chemical compounds that can be formed by replacing three of the six hydrogen atoms in a benzene ring with a <m>CH_3</m> radical.
              </p>
            </li>
          </ol>
        </p>

